headline: 3 Reasons to Sell UPS and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: Over the past six months, United Parcel Service’s shares (currently trading at $126.26) have posted a disappointing 6% loss, well below the S&P 500’s 10.4% gain. This may have investors wondering how to approach the situation.
